# Flight Booking System Dependencies

## Runtime Dependencies
bun ^1.0.0          # JavaScript/TypeScript runtime
elysia ^0.7.0       # Web framework for Bun
sqlite3 ^5.1.0      # SQLite database

## Development Dependencies
typescript ^5.0.0   # TypeScript language support
@types/bun ^1.0.0   # Type definitions for Bun
jest ^29.0.0        # Testing framework

## VS Code Extensions Required
- SQLite Viewer
- Thunder Client
- Bun
- TypeScript and JavaScript Language Features

## System Requirements
- Windows 10/11 with WSL2
- Node.js 16+ (for development tools)
- VS Code

## Database
- SQLite 3.x

## Environment Variables
PORT=3000
NODE_ENV=development

## Optional Tools
- Postman (for API testing)
- SQLite Browser (for database management)